*hpl-2.0-r3 (01 Jul 2013)

  01 Jul 2013; Justin Bronder <jsbronder@gentoo.org> -hpl-2.0-r1.ebuild,
  -hpl-2.0-r2.ebuild, +hpl-2.0-r3.ebuild:
  Respect CFLAGS (#452984). Remove old.

*hpl-2.0-r2 (27 Feb 2013)

  27 Feb 2013; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> hpl-2.0-r1.ebuild,
  +hpl-2.0-r2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Add missing dep on virtual/pkgconfig; use pc config to detect blas/lapack

  01 Feb 2011; Justin Bronder <jsbronder@gentoo.org> hpl-2.0-r1.ebuild:
  Bump EAPI thanks to scarabeus.

